text:
batik parses an empty selector as *, for example,

{background : red} as * {background : red}
a, {background : red} as a, * {background : red}
a, , b as a,*,b {background : red}

ideally these would be parsed like,

{background : red} as <nothing>
a, {background : red} as a {background : red}
a, , b as a, b {background : red}
